## Required Output

Produce a report with the following sections in this exact order. Use Markdown formatting.

IMPORTANT CONSTRAINTS:
- The attacker in this scenario is an UNPRIVILEGED THIRD PARTY — not the contract owner, not an admin, not any privileged role.
- The exploit MUST result in direct theft or permanent locking of funds (ETH, tokens, LP shares, or other on-chain value).
